name: Adak, Small Boat Harbor
content:
No this is not a mistake.  I have left my Padelesha hauled out in La Paz in order to come help my cousin sail his Cross 46 Trimaran, 'Migration', through the Aleutians.  Internet has been very limited so far so updates will be slow.

 Suffice it to say the adventures have been amazing and photos are coming very soon!
